Package com.ontotext.s4.api.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComponentConfigurationParameters
    Allows defining component parameters as key-value pairs using chained withConfigParameter(...) method calls and finally transforming those pairs to an object array that is accepted by the uimaFIT framework.
    FileUtils
    A util class representing common file operations.
    Preconditions
    A utility class expressing preconditions mostly for non nullness.
    TypeSystemUtils
    A utilities class giving functionality for generating and regenerating UIMA type system components as java classes and xml descriptors.
